1.0.name: wordpress/birdtips
1.0.description: BirdTIPS is a flexible three-column blog theme. The theme uses CSS3 media queries for its responsive layout and is therefore optimized for tablet pcs and smart phones. Features include the page navigation and breadcrumb navigation. You can also choose the link color, article title color and navigation menu color.
